zed ECG signals can serve\nas a potential tool for diagnosing COVID-19.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2022 16:44:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2022 15:05:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
