ficients, at\nCLIC (3 TeV, 5 ab$^{-1}$) and ILC (1 TeV, 8 ab$^{-1}$). We will then conclude\non the accessible region of these two parameters by studying the predicted\nrates at these two $e^+e^-$ colliders for the final state $b \\bar b b \\bar b\n\\nu \\bar \\nu$ leading to characteristic signals with 4 bottom jets and missing\nenergy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2022 17:16:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-04"}
