ing a route for efficient\noptical fiber interfaces. As a proof of concept, we demonstrate a frequency\nagile hybrid integrated III-V Lithium Niobate based laser with kHz linewidth\nand tuning rate of 0.7 Peta-Hertz per second with excellent linearity and\nCMOS-compatible driving voltage. Our approach can herald a new generation of\ntightly confining ferroelectric photonic integrated circuits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2022 20:47:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-12"}
