pervised approaches by a large margin, and after\nusing SCM for additional training, the model's performance was close to its\nfully supervised counterpart on the BraTS dataset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2022 07:00:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Feb 2023 08:40:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-14"}
