le vehicles. Moreover, integrating the proposed solution with the VANET\nrouting protocols improves routing efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2022 07:56:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-12"}
