e relationship between EEG and language; (2) visualizing\nword-level and sentence-level EEG-language alignment weights, showing the\ninfluence of different language semantics as well as EEG frequency features;\nand (3) visualizing brain topographical maps to provide an intuitive\ndemonstration of the connectivity of EEG and language response in the brain\nregions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2022 17:51:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 21 Aug 2022 01:37:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2022 19:10:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
